FWSAkRDRtools

File Management Tools for the Fish & Wildlife Service Alaska Regional Data Repository

Installation

You can install the development version of FWSAkRDRtools from GitHub with:

# Install devtools from CRAN
install.packages("devtools")

# Install FWSAkRDRtools from GitHub
devtools::install_github("hdvincelette/FWSAkRDRtools")

Getting help

Submit a GitHub Issue to report a bug and request a feature or enhancement. Contact the project maintainer for information about contributing to this project.
